{"tid":1886673,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人依家冇乜心機上堂？","createTime":"2020-02-19T05:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T06:54:38.000Z","uid":218353,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"471c7db9808f5b36b18df7b13dcf0e902fde50a6","tid":1886673,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:09:21.000Z","msg":"今年sem1  11月左右就唔使再返學， sem2開學返左一星期就放新年假， 新年假一完學校停埋課， 轉曬做online teaching<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原本sem2第一個星期啱啱好pickup返啲心情上堂就放假， 搞到online teaching冇乜心機上， 依家仲有啲lecture直情懶到係播片畀你班友睇， 越嚟越冇心機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最戇鳩係要準時剔返attendance， 依家八半基本上係起身剔完繼續瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人越嚟越廢"},{"pid":"a109344a941b214f85cbcff5186228b003ec86aa","tid":1886673,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"陣間四點半又要上堂， 我估過lecture又會再播片， 1630剔完 attendance就玩mon hun算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882a5835861010f812c3d97eee76ac9881cdfc95","tid":1886673,"uid":246694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:11:49.000Z","msg":"aame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c4b1d209be5c6b312aefd3a5fa0a52f06efb9f","tid":1886673,"uid":293093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0c35bc89e665d415c0ac4efcd891220c4d8108","tid":1886673,"uid":218353,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:14:47.000Z","msg":"正常都冇心機上堂啦， 個lecturer講嘢又廢， 隔離又咁撚大張床， 電腦又裝咗咁多game， 唔返學上堂嘅話冇可能可以正正常常咁上完一堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec36e11227d25a90df51b2a20ef359fb59b588cb","tid":1886673,"uid":321732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b0c35b